@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
@prev "Main"

 Introduction
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~

 NewHomer is a replacement for the funny but old Homer 1.6 found on Aminet.
 I wrote this program since the old version did not properly support truecolor
 screens when it tried to zoom the animation :(
 So here it is a replacement, fully compatible to the old one, but with
 many @{"enhancements" link "Enhancements" 0} that I hope you will like.

 Why did I bother doing such a program? First, because I'm a great fan of
 Simpsons and Homer in particular, second, because I still like this
 computer and its operating system, and all the joy that derives when you
 program it :)
@endnode

@node "Disclaimer" "Disclaimer"
@next "Requirements"
@prev "Introduction"

